item.title: CYM Camp 2010/2011
item.description: **CYM Melbourne & Geelong are pleased to invite all members, families and friends to our annual Camp. We have secured a wonderful facility at Phillip Island YMCA Discovery Camp as our temporary venue pending the rebuild of our bushfire affected oselya at Buxton “Karpaty “.** **Dates: **27th December 2010 – 2nd Jan 2011 **Venue: **73 - 77 Marlin Street, Smiths Beach Phillip Island, VIC, 3922 Bookings & Registrations (essential as this is a leased facility with capacity restrictions)
